  "contents": "<div class=\"content markitup-box\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t在李克强工作评价里强行插入 以习近平为核心。。。。<br/>\n<b>特别搞笑的是第一张图片里两次强行插入习近平那句话，仔细分析，已经变成了没有主语的病句</b><br/>\n<br/>\n<br/>\r\n但在疫情这一段，就没有亲自指挥亲自部署了。<br/>\n<br/>\r\n很简单，包子知道韭菜对口罩三年的政策有多恨。甩锅李克强。<br/>\n<a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly90ZWxlZ3JhLnBoL2ZpbGUvZTk0OTJmZDViOTZmYTNlYzc5YThlLnBuZz93aWR0aD0xMDgwJmhlaWdodD0yMjMz\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://telegra.ph/file/e9492fd5b96fa3ec79a8e.png?width=1080&amp;height=2233\"><img alt=\"https://telegra.ph/file/e9492fd5b96fa3ec79a8e.png?width=1080&amp;height=2233\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://telegra.ph/file/e9492fd5b96fa3ec79a8e.png?width=1080&amp;height=2233\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a><br/>\n<a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly90ZWxlZ3JhLnBoL2ZpbGUvNWVmYTk0OWUxZGMxYTYxNmFkYTFmLnBuZz93aWR0aD0xMDgwJmhlaWdodD0xNzk3\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://telegra.ph/file/5efa949e1dc1a616ada1f.png?width=1080&amp;height=1797\"><img alt=\"https://telegra.ph/file/5efa949e1dc1a616ada1f.png?width=1080&amp;height=1797\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://telegra.ph/file/5efa949e1dc1a616ada1f.png?width=1080&amp;height=1797\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a><br/>\r\n对比李鹏讣告，有提到坚持邓思想，但是对江泽民提到是中央领导集体。还是集体领导<br/>\r\n到了包子，就明牌了。一尊了。<br/>\n<a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly90ZWxlZ3JhLnBoL2ZpbGUvOWMyZWNmOWMwYTJlNGFmZWJkZDQzLnBuZz93aWR0aD0xMDgwJmhlaWdodD0yMTEz\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://telegra.ph/file/9c2ecf9c0a2e4afebdd43.png?width=1080&amp;height=2113\"><img alt=\"https://telegra.ph/file/9c2ecf9c0a2e4afebdd43.png?width=1080&amp;height=2113\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://telegra.ph/file/9c2ecf9c0a2e4afebdd43.png?width=1080&amp;height=2113\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a><br/>\n<a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly90ZWxlZ3JhLnBoL2ZpbGUvZTk1ODM3ODBlMjg4ZTdkYjU5MjQ1LnBuZz93aWR0aD0xMDgwJmhlaWdodD0yMjcy\" rel=\"nofollow